Package: slingshot-launcher
Architecture: any
Depends: zeitgeist-core, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Lightweight and stylish app launcher
 Slingshot is an application launcher for Pantheon,
 written in Vala and utilizing GTK+ and Cairo.
 .
 It features an optional category view and fast
 application search that uses Synapse as a back-end.
